                     Malevolent Creations - Main Menu

                          @{" Credits & Greetings " link "what"}


 The mind-blasting stuff itself:

 @{" -UNTITLED-      " system "data/0.dat data/1.dat blank reltime 10"}  See the alien devastating it's enemies!
 @{" AvaruusKolonia  " system "data/0.dat data/2.dat blank reltime 10"}  In space, the final frontier, weird things happen...
 @{" Dinosaurukset   " system "data/0.dat data/3.dat blank reltime 10"}  Watch in terror as the long gone animals walk on earth!
 @{" Kissa & Hiiri   " system "data/0.dat data/4.dat blank reltime 15"}  The Witch Duel
 @{" Kummitustalo    " system "data/0.dat data/5.dat blank reltime 10"}  Everything is twisted in this house of horrors!
 @{" Liquid Skulls   " system "data/0.dat data/6.dat blank reltime 3"}  Poor humans are slaughtered for money...
 @{" OtusLaboratorio " system "data/0.dat data/7.dat blank reltime 10"}  Unearthly creatures mate & spawn in this morbid lab!
 @{" Living Hills    " system "data/0.dat data/8.dat blank reltime 10"}  The hills are alive!
 @{" Valas           " system "data/0.dat data/9.dat blank reltime 10"}  Soon it will be killed by the greedy hunters...

              - Ruskean Reiän Ritarit / Pakasteena, kiitos -
